HEADWORD: Gristmill
<hw>Grist"mill"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A mill for
grinding grain; especially, a mill for grinding grists, or portions of
grain brought by different customers; a custom mill.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

